Bxc6 Bxc6 9. Re1
{ Later you will see that in 7...Ne7 line, after 8.Bxc6 Bxc6 I prefer  9.Qc2  but here I prefer the Queen on d2 as it protects the Knight on d4 and also makes Be3-h6 possible @@StartBracket@@at some point@@EndBracket@@. }
9... Bg7 10. d4 O-O
