11. dxe5 dxe5 12. Qc2
{ The Rook will come to d1, the Bishop can be developed to e3, d2 or even a3 @@StartBracket@@after a2-a4 and b2-b3@@EndBracket@@. The position is almost identical to the one arising from 6...g6. }
