20... Re8 21. Qd2
{ White has very nice compensation for the Pawn - Black's King is weakened, his light-squared Bishop is passive and also some of his Pawns are nice targets. The game might continue with  21...Qd6  22.h3  - we shouldn't be afraid of  22...Bxd4  23.Qxd4  Nf5  - White has great compensation in endgame too - we can just play  24.Qb6! }
