12. Kh1 b5 { Trying to provoke  13.Bxd3  again. } 13. Bb3
{ After this calm retreat it is becoming clear that Black has gained nothing - only weakened his position. The rest is more or less the same as in other lines - the Knight is coming to e4 giving White a nice initiative. }
