a5 13. Qd4 { The point of our previous move. } 13... f6
{ Due to e4-e5 there was no alternative. } 14. Bf4
{ We will develop our Knights to d2 and e3. The Queen shall retreat to d3 in order to avoid f6-f5 with tempo. After that, the Knight can come to d5. }
