{ Taking the Pawn with the Bishop gives White great advantage, but it's not impossible for Black to play this, especially if he misses our 19th move. }
18. Bxd6 Bxb2 19. Bxc5
{ It is practically winning already,  19...Bxa1  is answered with  20.Qxa1  threatening with mate so will capture the Rook as well. }
