16... Rad8
{ Logical and actually quite strong. The only problem is that now White can get a pleasant position practically by force. }
17. Qe1
{ This is a much better try than  17.Ng5  Bf5  where Black doesn't really have any problems. The Queen escaped from the possible pin @@StartBracket@@Be6-g4@@EndBracket@@ and now White really is threatening with Nf1-g3. }
