{ The threat is back but with the Knight on b7 it is no longer that serious. }
20. Re1 { Setting up a small trap. } 20... c5
{ Black is walking straight into it. This natural move blunders the most important Pawn in the position. }
21. Bg5 Rde8 22. Rxe5 c4
{ 22...Rxe5  23.Bf4  and there is nothing Black can do. } 23. Rxe8 Rxe8 24. Bd1
{ Black Knight is heading to d3 but it won't be enough to compensate White's domination on the dark-squares. }
