Qe6
{ 18...Nb4  loses by force after  19.Rxb4!  Bxb4  20.Rd1  Qe6  21.Be3!  This quiet retreat has a devastating effect - Black can't defend against Nd4 and Ng5. }
19. Rd1 { Black might be a Pawn up but the problem is he doesn't have a move. }
