13. d5 { It makes perfect sense once Rf8-e8 is played. } 13... Nb8
{ Logical move as the Knight is heading to d7. The only problem is that it drops a Pawn: }
14. Bxf6 Qxf6 15. axb5 axb5 16. Rxa8 Bxa8 17. Na3
{ The Knight will take the Pawn and then regroup to c4. } *

