13. Qd5
{ This is much stronger than  13.Bd5  where Black still has some chances after  13...Nxf2  . }
13... Be6 { Otherwise the Knight is just lost. } 14. Qxe4 Bxb3 15. Nd4
{ The point. Once again there are too many threats in the position to parry them all. }
15... O-O 16. Nxb3 Bb6 17. Nd4
{ White's position is too dominant for Black to survive it. } *

