14... Bb7 15. dxe5
{ After clearing out the situation in the center, White's light-squared Bishop will become even more powerful. }
15... Nxe5 { Solid but passive choice. } 16. Nxe5 Rxe5
{ It is often a good reaction but not here! } 17. Bxa7 Rxa7 18. f4 Re7 19. e5
{ We can now bring the Queen's Rook to e1 while the Queen can move to f2 with a tempo. White has a nice initiative. }
