fxe3 Nfd5 { 22...Nfd5  would allow  23.e6  with a strong initiative. } 23. Nde4
h6 24. Nc5 { This is stronger than  24.Nf3  Nb4  with unclear game. } 24...
hxg5 25. Nxb7 Qc8 26. Nc5 { Black now has to defend the Knight. } 26... c6 27.
e4
