20... Bxd5 21. exd5 Qg6
{ Black had to defend the Pawn on a6 but also the Queen is generally well placed on the 6th rank. }
22. Rad1
{ The Knight will soon come to e3 from where it will support the Pawn but will also be looking at f5 and c4. Black really has to be careful here. }
