11... Nxf3+ { This move is not very popular but actually it's quite strong. }
12. Qxf3 Be6 { Black decides to neutralize White's light square Bishop. } 13.
Bxe6 fxe6 { The f file is open so we should remove our Queen from it. } 14. Qh3
e5
{ Black could go  14...Qd7  instead but after  15.Nd2  his pieces would be cramped and it wouldn't be easy to come up with a good setup. }
