{ Taking with the Bishop is much stronger - now c7 becomes a target. } 17...
Nxb3 18. cxb3
{ Black can't really save the Pawn but we should know one useful trick: } 18...
Re8 19. Qxd8 Bxd8 { It seems that Black has managed to defend... } 20. Bd6
{ With this cute little move White wins a Pawn which should give him a slight edge. }
