{ Interfering with Black's plans - c7-c5 will need to be played anyway but then we will do en passant. }
13... Nd7 { An unfortunate try to activate the Knight. } 14. Bd2 Nd3
{ After  14...c5  15.dxc6  Nxc6  16.Nc3  Black's whole operation would be pointless. }
15. Re3 { Forcing Black to retreat the Knight. } 15... N3e5 16. Nd4
{ The black Knight can't find a safe place in the center as f2-f4 is coming. After  16...Bg5  we can just retreat,  17.Re1  . }
