{ Covering d4 but also giving some fresh air to the black Queen. } 21. Qd2
{ White is slightly better as our pieces are more active. Our plan is to attack on the Kingside - we can try h4-h5 for example. If Black plays  21...Re7  then most likely the idea will be to attack our Pawn with Qc8-e8. The simple  22.Re2  preparing 23.Rae1 will work then. }
