{ Surprisingly, this has never been played yet, probably Black is afraid of  11.a4  which is not so dangerous after all - Black has a decent reply -  11...a5  . }
11. Nc4 f6 12. a4
{ 12...a5  is no longer good due to  13.bxa5  Bxa5  14.Nxa5  Rxa5  15.Qe1!  followed by 16.Nh4. }
