18. Bh6 Rfe8 19. Qd2
{ This is not just a developing move as we had to stop  19...f5!?  - we now have  20.Bg5! }
19... d5 20. f3
{ We can put the Rook on g2 and then Nh4-f5 becomes a real threat. Black's position is unpleasant as he must constantly watch out for mating threats. }
