{ It is much stronger than  14.Rfd1  - we want to activate both Rooks! Black is already facing some serious problems, for instance  14...Rg8  is met with  15.e5!  dxe5  16.Qxe5  and in view of 17.Rad1 Black's position becomes critical. }
14... c5
{ Definitely not a pleasant decision but the pressure was too strong. } 15. Qd2
Qd7
{ Normally Qd8-e7 would be preferable but Black has to reckon with Nc3-d5. He also has to watch out for Nc3-b5. }
16. Rad1 O-O-O 17. Qf4
{ 17...Nh7  can be met with  18.Re3  threatening 19.Red3. Black's Pawn on g2 is a really good shelter for our King so let's not rush with taking it. }
