13. Nf1
{ A new idea. So far they all placed the Knight on b3. However it can be equally strong on the other side, especially now that the light-squared Bishop doesn't control f5. }
13... dxc3 14. bxc3 b4 { This is quite similar to 12...dxc3. } 15. Bb2 bxc3 16.
Bxc3 Bb4 { The same plan again... } 17. Qd2 a5 18. Rac1
