12... Bb7
{ This has to be considered, although  12...b4  seems both more logical and likely. }
13. Bg5 { Fighting for the d5-square. } 13... dxe4 14. dxe4 h6
{ 14...Qxd1  15.Rexd1  would only help White. } 15. Qxd8 Rexd8 16. Bxf6 gxf6
17. Ne3
