{ Another lovely trick, Black can't take the Rook as Be5xf6 would win. } 18...
Rxe5
{ Basically, it's the only move. After  18...Ne4  19.Nxf7!  would be winning. }
19. dxe5 h6 { Black survives the worst but he will not recover fully. } 20.
exf6 hxg5 21. fxg7 Bxg7 22. b3
{ White is clearly better as nothing can stop our Knight from reaching the f5-square. We can even go g2-g4 to support it. }
