16. Qd6
{ A beautiful strike! It is also a great example of how important the fianchettoed Bishop can be for the King's safety - as soon as it leaves its spot, the problems arrive. Black's position is collapsing. }
16... Nxc4
{ The only way to keep fighting.  16...Bxd6  leads to a mate after  17.Nxd6+  Kf8  18.Bh6+  Kg8  19.Bxf7#  . }
17. Qxc5
{ White is a piece down however, our Bishops are extremely powerful while Black's forces are still not ready for a fight. }
